iruna), Sweden to Victoria Island, northern Canada in June 2005; and a\n250-hour, circumpolar-flight from McMurdo Station, Antarctica, in December\n2006.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2007 21:48:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Mar 2008 16:18:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-07-03"}
